name: Kaosu
description: I was working with my sister the other day on some tie dye designs & noticed something, she kept telling me that the art of tie dying is a part of our DNA. At first I just agreed & continued on, but if you think about it she is correct. You take different colors, aggravators or toners and you randomly or strategically apply to parts of the shirt all twisted and smashed together. Isn't that exactly what the human race is? Beauty often comes from complete chaos, if only we could harness that power.  This photo is 3024x4032px 11.9mb & buyer gets 1/1 NFT & size small tie dyed t-shirt of this 1 & only hand painted, sparkled design shipped directly to physical address of your choice. *This will be the first piece in the new "Contour Colors" collection.
